{"tid":1419690,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同藍絲老豆打交，但佢講既野有啲得參考價值","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:23:44.000Z","uid":14583,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"72ab1090374fac6c8750ae8789b1c35c26f1408e","tid":1419690,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"廢話唔講<br />\n其中一個我老豆成為深藍既原因，就係比黃絲屌。<br />\n(雖然我覺得佢自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但係都有啲得著<br />\n<br />\n1. 繼續同普通市民&amp; 藍絲對鬧只會產生激進藍，就好似琴日仆街的士佬咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 既然可以鬧到變藍，亦都可以變翻淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學天琦話齋，對準政權，將其他人拉為己用<br />\n<br />\n其中一個我老豆比人屌既原因，就係佢話點解連儂牆唔可以有藍絲既版，既然講到學生咁想要言論自由，點解唔尊重其他人既言論自由。（我知係好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我先同佢嘈交）<br />\n<br />\n不過諗深一層都不無道理，既然我地恥笑毅仔冇學識，我地更加要表現出我地係civilized and well educated. 大家可以考慮係連儂牆主動加一小版位比藍絲貼，反正佢地都貼唔到咩花樣，又可以輕鬆嬴道德仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d3173d4f3cff1066d6c3a399c84b81ba3fbc89","tid":1419690,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:19:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"175a16bbb5cb0ac9a7eea8110d3b066620d2be5e","tid":1419690,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49921bdf722f4cb7381f6f601279e3ee21ef5ca4","tid":1419690,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68ddfb3eae4cef41c361217c0ee3bb2480db58a","tid":1419690,"uid":76558,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"不嬲都歡迎藍絲去貼  但佢地淨係識撕。。。"},{"pid":"f2a729591bf3fe7f5535ba20c6a8fea5d511e4b1","tid":1419690,"uid":45305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:21:46